snippet.title: Home Tour | Dhyan Sreenivasan | Luxury Big Budget Flat | Arpita | Parvathy Babu | Milestone Makers
snippet.description:
Home Tour | Dhyan Sreenivasan | Luxury Big Budget Flat | Arpita | Parvathy Babu | Milestone Makers

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films.Dhyan Sreenivasan was born on December 20, 1988 in Thalassery, Kerala, India. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

ഇണക്കുരുവികൾക്ക് മൊഞ്ചിലിന്ന് മംഗല നാള്  (തൻസീർ )

കൊട്ടും പാട്ടും മേളമോടെ വെട്ടമിന്നിതാ
മങ്കകൾ കരങ്ങൾ തട്ടി ചുറ്റുകൂടിതാ  (താജുദ്ധീൻ )

ചെക്കനരികെ പെണ്ണിരുന്നു നാണമോടിതാ (അത്തു )

ഹഖിലിന്ന് വന്നു ചേർന്നതൊക്കെയിന്നിതാ (നിസാം )

സൊറയും കളി ചിരിയും (മെഹ്രുന്നീസ )
കഥ പറയും മധു നിറയും (വിസ്മയ )

അതിലു മൃദുല മധുര ചിന്ത മിഥുനങ്ങൾക്കിതാ (സ്വിഫ്രാൻ, ഫിസ്ര )

മംഗല നാള് മംഗല നാള് ഇണക്കുരുവികൾക്ക് മൊഞ്ചിലിന്ന് മംഗല നാള് (സഹറാൻ , നൂറിൻ )

വെള്ളി നിലാവ് പൊന്നിൻ കിനാവ് പെണ്ണെ നീയൊരു പൂവ് (താജുദ്ധീൻ )
പൂവല് മെയ്യില് മൈലാഞ്ചി ചോപ്പില് മഞ്ചം നിറയെ വിരിക്കല് (നിസാം )

തട്ടമിട്ട ഹൂറിമാര് തൊട്ടടുത്തിതാ
തൊട്ടുരുമ്മി ചാരെ നിന്റെ ചെക്കനിന്നിതാ ( തൻസീർ )

മിന്നി മാഞ്ഞിതാ നിന്റെ പൂമുഖത്തെടി
മെല്ലെ കൊഞ്ചി വന്നത് മുഹബ്ബത്താണെടീ (അത്തു )

പല വർണ്ണ പന്തലിൽ വിരിഞ്ഞ പുഞ്ചിരി(ഫിസ്ര )
പതിനാലാം രാവു തോറ്റു പോകും മഞ്ചരി(സിഫ്രാൻ )
പുലരുന്ന നാള് പുളകമല്ലേ പുന്നാരീ (വിസ്മയ, മെഹ്‌റു )

കോറസ് പല്ലവി ഫുൾ
(എല്ലാരും പാടണം )

വിണ്ണിലെ താരം മണ്ണിലിറങ്ങുന്ന മിന്നിടും മംഗല്യ നാളിതാ (വിസ്മയ )
ലങ്കിടും പൊന്നിൻ ചൊങ്കില് പെണ്ണ് മൊഞ്ചത്തിയായ് ചമഞ്ഞിതാ (അത്തു )

കനവ് കണ്ട പെണ്മണിക്ക് മാരനിന്നിതാ (മെഹറുനിസ )
കവിളിൽ പൂത്ത നാണ നുണക്കുഴി തെളിഞ്ഞിതാ (നിസാം )

പട്ടു മെത്ത കൊണ്ടലങ്കരിച്ച മണിയറ 
കൊട്ടിയടച്ചിട്ടു പുൽകിടുന്ന കലവറ (തൻസീർ )

കാത്തിരുന്ന തോഴനിന്ന് അത്തറു പൂശി ( സിഫ്രാൻ, സഹറാൻ )
ഒത്തു ചേർന്ന് പന്തലില് പുഞ്ചിരി വീശി ( ഫിസ്ര, നൂറിൻ )
ഹുസുനുൽ ജമാലിനൊത്ത ബദറുൽ മുനീറ് ( താജുദ്ധീൻ )

പൂവല് മെയ്യില് മൈലാഞ്ചി ചോപ്പില് മഞ്ചം നിറയെ വിരിക്കല് (നിസാം )

തട്ടമിട്ട ഹൂറിമാര് തൊട്ടടുത്തിതാ
തൊട്ടുരുമ്മി ചാരെ നിന്റെ ചെക്കനിന്നിതാ ( തൻസീർ )

മിന്നി മാഞ്ഞിതാ നിന്റെ പൂമുഖത്തെടി
മെല്ലെ കൊഞ്ചി വന്നത് മുഹബ്ബത്താണെടീ (അത്തു )

പല വർണ്ണ പന്തലിൽ വിരിഞ്ഞ പുഞ്ചിരി(ഫിസ്ര )
പതിനാലാം രാവു തോറ്റു പോകും മഞ്ചരി(സിഫ്രാൻ )
പുലരുന്ന നാള് പുളകമല്ലേ പുന്നാരീ (വിസ്മയ, മെഹ്‌റു )

കോറസ് പല്ലവി ഫുൾ
(എല്ലാരും പാടണം )

വിണ്ണിലെ താരം മണ്ണിലിറങ്ങുന്ന മിന്നിടും മംഗല്യ നാളിതാ (വിസ്മയ )
ലങ്കിടും പൊന്നിൻ ചൊങ്കില് പെണ്ണ് മൊഞ്ചത്തിയായ് ചമഞ്ഞിതാ (അത്തു )

കനവ് കണ്ട പെണ്മണിക്ക് മാരനിന്നിതാ (മെഹറുനിസ )
കവിളിൽ പൂത്ത നാണ നുണക്കുഴി തെളിഞ്ഞിതാ (നിസാം )

പട്ടു മെത്ത കൊണ്ടലങ്കരിച്ച മണിയറ 
കൊട്ടിയടച്ചിട്ടു പുൽകിടുന്ന കലവറ (തൻസീർ )

കാത്തിരുന്ന തോഴനിന്ന് അത്തറു പൂശി ( സിഫ്രാൻ, സഹറാൻ )
ഒത്തു ചേർന്ന് പന്തലില് പുഞ്ചിരി വീശി ( ഫിസ്ര, നൂറിൻ )
ഹുസുനുൽ ജമാലിനൊത്ത ബദറുൽ മുനീറ് ( താജുദ്ധീൻ )

snippet.description:
திருதியை திதி 22 & 23-04-2023 ஆகிய 2 தேதிகளிலும் இருப்பதால் பொருட்கள் வாங்குவது, தானம் போன்றவற்றை 22-04-2023-ஆம் தேதியிலும் செய்யலாம்.  வீடு பால் காய்ச்சுதல், வீடு குடி புகுதல், வாஸ்து போன்றவற்றை 23-04-2023 தேதியில் செய்வதே சிறந்தது.  அன்றைய தினத்திலேயே  பொருட்கள் வாங்குவது & தானம் தருதல் போன்றவற்றையும் செய்யலாம்.

snippet.description:

In Cinemas 18th May
Advance Booking Now Open.

Director: Louis Leterrier

Writer: Dan Mazeau
Producer: Neal H. Moritz
Producer: Vin Diesel
Producer/Writer: Justin Lin
Producer: Jeff Kirschenbaum
Producer: Samantha Vincent
Executive Producer: Joseph M. Caracciolo Jr.
Executive Producer: David Cain
Executive Producer: Chris Morgan
Executive Producer: Amanda Lewis
Executive Producer: Mark Bomback
Cast: Vin Diesel, Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris “Ludacris” Bridges, Jason Momoa, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, John Cena, Jason Statham, Sung Kang, Alan Ritchson, Daniela Melchior, Scott Eastwood, with Helen Mirren, Charlize Theron, Brie Larson and Rita Moreno

The end of the road begins. 

Fast X, the tenth film in the Fast & Furious Saga, launches the final chapters of one of cinema’s most storied and popular global franchises, now in its third decade and still going strong with the same core cast and characters as when it began.

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they’ve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who’s fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything—and everyone—that Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011’s Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn’t know was that Reyes’ son, Dante (Aquaman’s Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante’s plot will scatter Dom’s family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante’s vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris “Ludacris” Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar® winner Helen Mirren and Oscar® winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar® winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn’t hold the same fondness for Dom’s crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom’s past; and legendary Oscar® winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia’s Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback.

Tere Bin Episode 34 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 20th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

snippet.title: Starship Flight Test
snippet.description:
Starship gave us quite a show during today’s first flight test of a fully integrated Starship and Super Heavy rocket from Starbase in Texas. 
 
At 8:33 a.m. CT, Starship successfully lifted off from the orbital launch pad for the first time. The vehicle cleared the pad and beach as Starship climbed to an apogee of ~39 km over the Gulf of Mexico – the highest of any Starship to-date. The vehicle experienced multiple engines out during the flight test, lost altitude, and began to tumble. The flight termination system was commanded on both the booster and ship. As is standard procedure, the pad and surrounding area was cleared well in advance of the test, and we expect the road and beach near the pad to remain closed until tomorrow.

With a test like this, success comes from what we learn, and we learned a tremendous amount about the vehicle and ground systems today that will help us improve on future flights of Starship.
 
Thank you to our customers, Cameron County, and the wider community for the continued support and encouragement. And congratulations to the entire SpaceX team on an exciting first flight test of Starship!

snippet.title: First 1000 Days | Awareness | Dreamz Unlimted
snippet.description:
Why first 1000 days is so important in child' s life? 
This is because the developing brain of a child grows and develops throughout the first 1,000 days. This is also the period when the foundations for their long-term health are set [1]. Children's brains can create 1,000 new neural connections every second throughout this time.

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3750 - 20 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3750: Car Coupon ka Sach
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak meets Jetha at the garden to discuss the issue of the car coupon, Taarak comes up with another idea that they should take help from Sodhi and arrange another same model car to show Babita and other Gokuldham members which will give them a few more days to think about the car coupon. Jetha denies the idea as he thinks that he can be charged with fraud as Babita will be posting the car photos on social media. Taarak comes with the last idea that they should confront Rustom Ji and tell them the truth about the coupon. What happens next? Stay tuned to know what happens with Babita's car coupon!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3750, 20 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Tere Bin Episode 33 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 19th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.title: SpaceX Starship rocket blows up minutes after launch
snippet.description:
The largest and most powerful rocket ever built blasted off from Texas but blew up within minutes, in a test flight that its makers, SpaceX, hope will be the first step on a human journey to Mars. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

After a cancelled launch earlier this week due to a pressurisation issue, the 120-metre Starship rocket system took off at 8.33am local time on Thursday. It gathered speed but then started to spin at altitude before exploding about four minutes after leaving the ground. It appeared that the two sections of the rocket system – the booster and cruise vessel – were unable to separate properly after takeoff, possibly causing the spacecraft to fail.

snippet.description:
HealthySummerladduRecipe  #summerladduRecipe   Healthy summer laddu Recipe  which is Immunity booster ladoo recipe. summers special immunity boost laddu jo banaye aapko healthy and fit, coconut and dry fruits laddu. summers special healthy and tasty laddu jo ki hai coconut and dry fruits laddu. easy and tasty laddu recipe khaas garmiyon ke liye. garmiyon me khaas thandak dene vale laddu learn  how to make coconut and dry fruits laddu.Laddu for strength immunity and reducing headache.

#laddurecipe #healthyladdurecipe #ladoorecipe #laddu #ladoo #laddoorecipe #healthyladdu #proteinladdu #weightlosssnack #weightlossrecipe #coconutladoo 

Share 📱📞this Tasty Recipe with Friends and Family on - 📗 Whatsapp 
⏩𝓢𝓾𝓫𝓼𝓬𝓻𝓲𝓫𝓮 my channel:💖 https://goo.gl/n9nvav  ☑️🙂Press Bell 🔔
📕 https://www.youtube.com/CookWithParul/ 
📙 https://www.instagram.com/cookwithparul/  
#cookwithparul #cookwithparulrecipe 

Ingredients List: 🍕🍣 सामग्री 
🌐  Full Written Recipe🍕 Step by Step Visit my Website  https://cookwithparul.com/ 
🌐  पूरी लिखित रेसिपी 🍣 देखने के लिए आप मेरी हिंदी वेबसाइट लिंक को क्लिक कीजिये  Hindi Website  https://cookwithparul.com/hi/
* Lotus Seeds/Fox Nuts/Phool Makhana - 25 gm
* Musk Melon Seeds - 1/2 cup
* Almonds बादाम - 1/4 cup
* Cashew nut काजू - 1/4 cup
* Dates खजूर - 1/2 cup
* Clarified Butter घी - 2 tbsp
* Black Pepper Powder काली मिर्च पाउडर - 1/4 tsp
* Desiccated Coconut - 2 cup
* Cardamom Powder इलाइची - 1/2 tsp
* Mishri मिश्री - 1 cup
* Water पानी - 3/4 cup
* Pistachio पिस्ता - 1 tbsp

HealthySummerladduRecipe  #summerladduRecipe   Healthy summer laddu Recipe  which is Immunity booster ladoo recipe. summers special immunity boost laddu jo banaye aapko healthy and fit, coconut and dry fruits laddu. summers special healthy and tasty laddu jo ki hai coconut and dry fruits laddu. easy and tasty laddu recipe khaas garmiyon ke liye. garmiyon me khaas thandak dene vale laddu learn  how to make coconut and dry fruits laddu.Laddu for strength immunity and reducing headache.

#laddurecipe #healthyladdurecipe #ladoorecipe #laddu #ladoo #laddoorecipe #healthyladdu #proteinladdu #weightlosssnack #weightlossrecipe #coconutladoo 

Share 📱📞this Tasty Recipe with Friends and Family on - 📗 Whatsapp 
⏩𝓢𝓾𝓫𝓼𝓬𝓻𝓲𝓫𝓮 my channel:💖 https://goo.gl/n9nvav  ☑️🙂Press Bell 🔔
📕 https://www.youtube.com/CookWithParul/ 
📙 https://www.instagram.com/cookwithparul/  
#cookwithparul #cookwithparulrecipe 

Ingredients List: 🍕🍣 सामग्री 
🌐  Full Written Recipe🍕 Step by Step Visit my Website  https://cookwithparul.com/ 
🌐  पूरी लिखित रेसिपी 🍣 देखने के लिए आप मेरी हिंदी वेबसाइट लिंक को क्लिक कीजिये  Hindi Website  https://cookwithparul.com/hi/
* Lotus Seeds/Fox Nuts/Phool Makhana - 25 gm
* Musk Melon Seeds - 1/2 cup
* Almonds बादाम - 1/4 cup
* Cashew nut काजू - 1/4 cup
* Dates खजूर - 1/2 cup
* Clarified Butter घी - 2 tbsp
* Black Pepper Powder काली मिर्च पाउडर - 1/4 tsp
* Desiccated Coconut - 2 cup
* Cardamom Powder इलाइची - 1/2 tsp
* Mishri मिश्री - 1 cup
* Water पानी - 3/4 cup
* Pistachio पिस्ता - 1 tbsp

snippet.description:
#lokeshkanagaraj #suriya #jaibhim  #avcinemaawards #vikatanawards #cinemavikatan #Vikatancinemaawards  

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

snippet.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

कुछ दिन पहले दिल्ली विश्वविद्यालय के 'श्रीराम कॉलेज ऑफ कॉमर्स' के विद्यार्थियों ने अपने बिजनेस कॉन्क्लेव में आमंत्रित किया था। वहॉं की चर्चा इसी बिंदु पर केंद्रित रही कि पढ़ाई के बाद नौकरी करना बेहतर है या अपना कोई उद्यम शुरू किया जाए! इसी क्रम में यह भी बात हुई कि उद्यम ही शुरू किया जाए तो किस तरह का उद्यम अधिक उपयोगी और लाभकारी हो सकता है तथा सही निर्णय लेने के लिये किन बिंदुओं का ध्यान रखना चाहिये।


मुझे लगता है कि आपमें से ज़्यादातर लोगों के मन में भी यह दुविधा होती ही होगी, तो आज यही बातचीत आपसे साझा कर रहा हूँ। उम्मीद है कि इससे आपको अपने पेशेवर जीवन के लिये कुछ उपयोगी सूत्र मिल सकेंगे। 

शुभकामनाओं सहित, 
विकास दिव्यकीर्ति


Dear Viewers,

A few days ago, the students of Delhi University's 'Shri Ram College of Commerce' had invited me to their Business Conclave. The discussion there focused on the point that is it better to do a job after studies or to start an enterprise of your own! In the same sequence, it was also discussed that if the enterprise is started, then what kind of enterprise can be more useful and beneficial and what points should be kept in mind to take the right decision.


I think most of you must have this dilemma in your mind too, so today I am sharing this conversation with you. Hope this gives you some useful tips for your professional life.

with best wishes,
Vikas Divyakirti

snippet.title: The Song Of Scorpions - Official Trailer | Irrfan Khan | Golshifteh Farahani | Anup Singh
snippet.description:
The Song of Scorpions is a story of twisted love, revenge and the redemptive power of a song. Nooran, carefree and defiantly independent, is a tribal woman learning the ancient art of healing from her grandmother, a revered scorpion-singer. When Aadam, a camel trader in the Rajasthan desert, hears her sing, he falls desperately in love. But even before they can get to know each other better, Nooran is poisoned by a treachery that sets her on a perilous journey to avenge herself and find her song.

#TheSongOfScorpions Official Trailer out now.
In Cinemas 28th April 2023.

#irrfankhan #golshiftehfarahani

snippet.description:

 ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
Salman Khan along with his co-actor Pooja Hegde makes a royal entry on the sets in between the full shouting of the audience. Kapil praises Salman's new film 'Kisi Ke Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan' and his role in Pathan. He also mentions the huge fan following of Salman Khan. Then they had a fun-filled conversation about the ice cream candies. How will Kapil entertain them, Watch the episode and know more!!

snippet.description:
With Pathaan and Tiger in the same frame, goosebumps are guaranteed! Watch them in action with the Pathaan x Tiger theme, video out now!

About YRF Spy Universe: 
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise. 

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali! 

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3749 - 19 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3749: Taarak Ka Tedha Idea
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom Ji calls Bagha to ask about the reason for his call to Dolly. Bagha tells Rustom Ji that he had called Dolly to ask her about the color of Babita Ji's car. Jetha intervenes and starts to talk to Rustom Ji, which makes him angry. Rustom Ji realizes that Bagha has been talking to him on speakers, which makes him really upset. Later, Rustom Ji gives an ultimatum that by 6 p.m. he needs the coupon delivered to his office; otherwise, the prize will be canceled. Out of anxiety, Jetha immediately calls Tarrak for help. Unfortunately, Taarak has been talking to his boss when he gets Jetha's call, and that is why he disconnects the call. What happens next? Stay tuned to know what happens with Babita's car coupon!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3749, 19 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000217282

snippet.title: INSIDIOUS: THE RED DOOR – Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
It ends where it all began. 🚪 Watch the trailer for Insidious: The Red Door, exclusively in theaters this July. #InsidiousMovie

In Insidious: The Red Door, the horror franchise’s original cast returns for the final chapter of the Lambert family’s terrifying saga. To put their demons to rest once and for all, Josh (Patrick Wilson) and a college-aged Dalton (Ty Simpkins) must go deeper into The Further than ever before, facing their family’s dark past and a host of new and more horrifying terrors that lurk behind the red door.
 
The original cast from Insidious is back with Patrick Wilson (also making his directorial debut), Ty Simpkins, Rose Byrne, and Andrew Astor. Also starring Sinclair Daniel and Hiam Abbass. Produced by Jason Blum, Oren Peli, James Wan and Leigh Whannell. The screenplay is written by Scott Teems from a story by Leigh Whannell, based on characters created by Leigh Whannell.
 
Insidious: The Red Door Opens July 7th.  
 
Directed by: Patrick Wilson
 
Screenplay by: Scott Teems
 
Story by: Leigh Whannell
 
Based on characters created by: Leigh Whannell 
 
Produced by:

James Wan
Leigh Whannell

and Rose Byrne

snippet.title: Vijay Raaz Comedy - बैग मे बाबाजी का घंटा है.. देखना है ? Rajpal Yadav Comedy | HD COMEDY SCENES
snippet.description:
Criminals Hazari (Sanjay Mishra) and Murari (Rajpal Yadav) rob the Police Commissioner's home, and Chetta Singh (Vijay Raaz) steal the car belonging to the Commissioner's wife, Kusum (Rati Agnihotri). Meanwhile, AD (Aftab Shivdasani) elopes with Shreya (Priyanka Kothari), the niece of Police Sub-Inspector Pralay Pratap Singh (Om Puri). With each group is on the run for different reasons, they all end up in a vehicle stolen from crime boss Durjan Singh/Black Cobra (Gulshan Grover). In the vehicle is a suitcase filled with Durjan's loot.

Sanjay Mishra Comedy - क्या घंटा सही कर रहा है सर | राजपाल यादव और संजय मिश्रा की लोटपोट कॉमेडी 

Movie - Bin Bulaye Baraati 
StarCast - Aftab Shivdasani, Priyanka Kothari, Rajpal Yadav, Sanjay Mishra, Om Puri, Vijay Raaz
Director - Chandrakant Singh
Producer - Dhanraj Jethani, Dhanraj Films
Cinematography - Johny Lal
Editor - Pranav Dhiwar, pankaj sharma

#binbulayebaraaticomedymovie #rajpalyadavcomedy #vijayraazcomedy 

अपराधी हजारी (संजय मिश्रा) और मुरारी (राजपाल यादव) पुलिस आयुक्त के घर को लूटते हैं, और चेट्टा सिंह (विजय राज) आयुक्त की पत्नी कुसुम (रति अग्निहोत्री) की कार चुराते हैं। इस बीच, एडी (आफताब शिवदासानी) पुलिस सब-इंस्पेक्टर प्रलय प्रताप सिंह (ओम पुरी) की भतीजी श्रेया (प्रियंका कोठारी) के साथ भाग जाता है। प्रत्येक समूह अलग-अलग कारणों से भाग रहा है, वे सभी क्राइम बॉस दुर्जन सिंह / ब्लैक कोबरा (गुलशन ग्रोवर) से चुराए गए वाहन में समाप्त हो जाते हैं। वाहन में दुर्जन की लूट से भरा एक सूटकेस है।

फिल्म- बिन बुलाए बाराती
स्टारकास्ट - आफताब शिवदासानी, प्रियंका कोठारी, राजपाल यादव, संजय मिश्रा, ओम पुरी, विजय राज
निर्देशक - चंद्रकांत सिंह
निर्माता - धनराज जेठानी, धनराज फिल्म्स
छायांकन - जॉनी लाल
संपादक - प्रणव धीवर, पंकज शर्मा

snippet.title: Exploring Seven Bungalows, Andheri With Honey Singh | Tere Gully Mein Ep 39 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
In this episode, we are exploring the streets of Seven Bungalows, Andheri with popular rapper Yo Yo Honey Singh. 

This Delhi boy is in for a treat as we tempt him with some of Mumbai's finest delicacies, including the ever-popular Mumbaiya Chat at Chandru's Pure Ghee Sweets and the flavorful Misal at Thorat's Baarbeque Misal. 

While there was a lot of talk about food he also shared his journey towards fame in the music industry, the struggles he faced with depression and how it affected his personal and professional life. He spoke about his upcoming projects, and much more. 

We had a gala time as we dive into the heart of Mumbai's street food scene with a hip-hop legend by our side. Hope you enjoyed watching the video too!!!

en-GB.description:
In this episode, we are exploring the streets of Seven Bungalows, Andheri with popular rapper Yo Yo Honey Singh. 

This Delhi boy is in for a treat as we tempt him with some of Mumbai's finest delicacies, including the ever-popular Mumbaiya Chat at Chandru's Pure Ghee Sweets and the flavorful Misal at Thorat's Baarbeque Misal. 

While there was a lot of talk about food he also shared his journey towards fame in the music industry, the struggles he faced with depression and how it affected his personal and professional life. He spoke about his upcoming projects, and much more. 

We had a gala time as we dive into the heart of Mumbai's street food scene with a hip-hop legend by our side. Hope you enjoyed watching the video too!!!

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part -487 | Kya Balram Banaayenge Laddoo? #starbharat

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

TRS is now AJIO Presents TRS: https://bit.ly/3A8lKBm 

One of the biggest announcements of my career :
I honestly began this podcast because of a breakup! 

Didn't know what to do about the anger and emotion I was feeling back then. Therefore instead of shutting down my YouTube channel, I gave it one last shot.

After almost 500 podcasts, we've become India's first independently produced talk show that's now backed by a title partner!!! 

TRS is now AJIO Presents TRS!

Some of our most stellar work is going to be released over the next few weeks! 

Watch out for it 🔥 
And keep supporting the show, because we are far from done 😉

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3748 - 18 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3748: Sihayi Hatane Ka Idea
--------------------------------------------------------
To find out more about Babita Ji's car, Bagha phones Dolly, Rustom's assistant. When Bagha asks Dolly what hue the car is, she reveals that it is red. Bagha advises Jetha to create a replica coupon and submit it to the Ramsang company despite Jetha's brooding about the broken coupon. Jetha calls Taarak to get advice on creating a fake coupon. As an alternative, Taarak offers suggestions for ink removal. Will Jetha, therefore, be able to obtain a fresh forgery of a coupon, or will he be able to remove the ink? Remain tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3748, 18 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. Pehli nazar ka pyaar or Love at first sight is often considered to be an eternal truth for most of the relationships jahan ek jhalak mei hi pata lag jaata hai ki humein apna life partner mil gaya!
Kya hoga agar aap and ek din kisi cafe mei jao aur aapko apna pehli nazar wala pyar randomly wahan miljaaye? And on top of that He/She is the owner of the cafe!
Ek aisi hi anokhi jodi ki mulaqaat hui ek cafe mei jahan do dil mile aur baat ban gayi!

Watch the video till the end to know what goes on when you start dating a cafe owner.

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!
